<plot>Of the three brothers living together in a tiny apartment, only the eldest is holding down a job and putting any food on the table. Even so, he gets almost no respect from his siblings, who mock him and order him around constantly. Despite this, he still seems happy to support them. When the two younger brothers discover that their elder brother has a girlfriend, they devise a plot to amuse themselves once again at his expense. Will their prank go too far this time?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?104387</url></doc>
